=head1 Quick'n'dirty hacks

Small scripts to solve small problems

=head1 nim/

=head2 lsnim.pl

Script to sort output of "lsnim -t lpp_source" which is useful when
it's called by a NIM client.

=head1 linux/lvm/

=head2 chfs.pl

Script to simulate "chfs -a size=..." for a Linux LVM
